(Lehm.) Geissler &amp; Gradst. subsp. 
<emphasis id="B900EA88491A0D25FF3CB837FE9AF999" bold="true" box="[136,260,1580,1604]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">ludoviciana</emphasis>
